Kajiado Central MP Elijah Kanchory Memusi's wife, Mrs Stella Memusi, has died in a road accident this morning along the Nairobi-Namanga road.  Kajiado police commander Muthuri Mwongera says the vehicle that was carrying her rammed into a lorry killing her on the spot.  The driver was also injured and was rushed to the hospital in critical condition.  More to follow... Â   By Julius Chepkwony | 18 hours ago By Standard Team | 21 hours ago By Kennedy Gachuhi | 1 day ago By Christopher Kipsang and Obare Osinde | 1 day ago